{"name":"Severus Snape","nameCn":"西弗勒斯·斯内普","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/3b/c5/75764_crt_T0oJ2.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>西弗勒斯·斯内普</li><li><span>别名: </span>賽佛勒斯·石內卜</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>セブルス・スネイプ</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>混血王子、鼻涕精</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li><li><span>生日: </span>1960年1月9日</li><li><span>出生地区: </span>蜘蛛尾巷，科克沃斯，英国</li><li><span>死亡日期: </span>1998年5月2日</li>","detail":"西弗勒斯·斯内普（1960年1月9日－1998年5月2日）是霍格沃茨魔法学校的魔药学教授和斯莱特林学院院长。1996年起开始担任黑魔法防御术教授，并在1997年到1998年担任校长。是全系列故事中一个重要的角色。<br /><br />他表面上很不喜欢哈利·波特，却因对莉莉·伊万丝的爱，因而答应邓布利多而一直暗中保护哈利；但斯内普内心认为哈利跟他父亲一样“骄傲自大”，而在学校中对他百般刁难。实际上斯内普扮演双面间谍的身份，后被伏地魔所杀，最终证明他对莉莉·伊万丝的绝对忠心和不求回报的爱。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/78306","name":"Harry Potter","nameCn":"哈利·波特","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/51/5a/78306_qhf59.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/60119","name":"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets","nameCn":"哈利·波特与密室","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/c8/7a/60119_56prO.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"Alan Rickman","castHref":"/person/39647","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/de/54/39647_prsn_CmsZ7.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/60118","name":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","nameCn":"哈利·波特与阿兹卡班囚徒","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/6b/9f/60118_4ew2z.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"Alan Rickman","castHref":"/person/39647","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/de/54/39647_prsn_CmsZ7.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/60107","name":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","nameCn":"哈利·波特与火焰杯","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/17/8b/60107_EXHDm.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"Alan Rickman","castHref":"/person/39647","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/de/54/39647_prsn_CmsZ7.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/60106","name":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","nameCn":"哈利·波特与凤凰社","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/39/d9/60106_ywuCM.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"Alan Rickman","castHref":"/perso